rl=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471990-20190801.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6d670cd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471990-20190801.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n3人涉藏爆炸品被捕　警方稱警署外放煙花案是調查方向<br />\n2019-08-01 HKT 23:43<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/videos/vfile_1471990_1_20190802000355.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fvideos%2Fvfile_1471990_1_20190802000355.mp4&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=28aaa86f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/videos/vfile_1471990_1_20190802000355.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方在天水圍天瑞邨一個單位，搜出一批自製的煙霧彈，拘捕單位內兩女一男，涉嫌無牌藏有爆炸品。<br />\n<br />\n有組織罪案及三合會調查科警司楊耀宗表示，下午近5時根據線報搜查單位，找到30枚煙霧彈、半製成品、硝酸鉀等原材料和工具。<br />\n<br />\n被捕人士分別是母親和她的一子一女，年齡介乎23至47歲，要進一步調查誰人藏有煙霧彈，以及和最近示威遊行是否有關，又說早前天水圍警署外有人向人群放煙花的案件，是其中一個調查方向。至於煙霧彈的威力，楊耀宗說要由爆炸品處理課進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n-----------<br />\n似乎唔關煙花事，似係初心者手作之店"},{"pid":"22321ef90c491476be34b1c6d1899e52aae7ee1f","tid":1394803,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:21:15.000Z","msg":"點解冇人天水圍吹雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3b14bf3fe646cb21bd1063e4ffb06dcd7bcf9f","tid":1394803,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"線報係原材料賣家？定係海關檢查可疑物品？定係佢鄰居？"},{"pid":"5511d2a09444b2d74c076e61fd54d3ecfc73de4c","tid":1394803,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:23:37.000Z","msg":"wd40"}]}